\b\fs32 \cf0 Application Shell
\b0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\ql\qnatural

\fs22 \cf0 \
The Application Shell for the Customer Needs Management application will consist of three areas; the Global Action Bar, Content Area and the Page Action Bar. \'a0This simple shell matches the simplicity of this application and will help create a consistent experience throughout the application. \'a0The application has been designed to the resolution of 1024 x 768 (mock-ups are slightly smaller to account for task bar, etc...). \'a0Below are the design goals and xnotes for the Application Shell\
\
1. Provide simple and clear global navigation of the application\
2. Maximize the vertical and horizontal space allocated to content\
\pard\pardeftab720\ql\qnatural
\cf2 3. Minimize work on the user part (cognitive, memory, visual and physical work)\cf0 \
\
