\ul Object Details\ulnone \
The Object Details page will display all of the details of a selected User object. \'a0The Object Details page will be made up of two main areas, the Structure Explorer and the Object Information. \'a0The Structure Explorer will display the structure that the user object belongs within. \'a0The user can then use the structure to view other related objects. \'a0The Structure Explorer behavior notes are detailed is a separate document. \'a0The Object Information area includes 6 main sections that will also be detailed in a separate document. \'a0 \'a0\
